{"tid":1900391,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ff系列 - 隔離檢疫期間有糧出","createTime":"2020-02-27T07:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T13:27:45.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0602a869eb15aae7d3b0420ff19ad743ba980e18","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"有冇老細想還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Yl8RXID.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYl8RXID.jpg&h=c0c12318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/26/P2020022600477.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F26%2FP2020022600477.htm&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=845327d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/26/P2020022600477.htm</a><br />\n以下是今日（二月二十六日）在立法會會議上蔣麗芸議員的提問：<br />\n（七）鑑於政府呼籲由內地返港的市民，應在回港後盡量自我隔離14天，<span style=\"color: red;\">會否就僱主可否把因自我隔離而沒有上班的員工視為放取假期或扣減該等員工的薪酬發出指引</span>；<br />\n <br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始教授的書面答覆：<br />\n（七）由二○二○年二月八日凌晨起，衞生署根據《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》（第599C章），要求從內地入境的人士或從外地入境但在過去14天內曾到訪內地的人士，包括香港居民、內地居民和其他旅客，均須強制接受檢疫14天，擅自離開會構成刑事罪行。《僱傭條例》（第57章）就自我隔離的員工的假期或工資安排<span style=\"color: red;\">並無作出法定規例</span>。然而，政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鼓勵</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />僱主體恤和諒解僱員的情況，作出<span style=\"color: red;\">彈性</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />處理。<br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n羅致光網誌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.lwb.gov.hk/tc/blog/post_09022020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fblog%2Fpost_09022020.html&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=b9dfa468\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lwb.gov.hk/tc/blog/post_09022020.html</a><br />\n在勞工角度，部分僱主僱員難免會受影響，勞工處已發出新聞稿解釋，如果僱員染病，僱主須根據《僱傭條例》或有關的僱傭合約，讓該僱員放取病假。如僱員被衞生主任要求或命令接受檢疫，衞生主任會為該僱員發出醫生證明書；<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府鼓勵僱主體恤和諒解</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有關僱員的情況，作出彈性處理，包括在可行情況下容許僱員在家工作或讓他放取有薪假期，這有助維持良好的勞資關係及保障所有僱員及社會大眾的健康。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n須隔離員工無薪 九巴被指反口<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200216/s00001/1581789951834/%E9%A0%88%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA-%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200216%2Fs00001%2F1581789951834%2F%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2596%25AA-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=57cc60ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200216%2Fs00001%2F1581789951834%2F%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2596%25AA-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3&h=a55e8578\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200216/s00001/1581789951834/%E9%A0%88%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA-%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3</a><br />\n<blockquote>2003年SARS期間，勞工處曾發指引，如衛生署長向僱員發出隔離令，《僱傭條例》有薪病假的要求及安排同樣適用。職工盟秘書長李卓人透露，兩周前曾與勞福局長羅致光溝通，對方稱經研究條例後，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現法例的有薪病假類別中沒有「隔離」一項，羅形容當年決定「是錯」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />李卓人建議政府可研究修例，或由政府補償被隔離或檢疫而未獲有薪假期的僱員。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"23d09f5ed281fb5e4aa6ef80a40dee9b18669fbc","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"欠債要靠賭博來還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/02-26-2020/t_ae2d969d287745a1922d504d42748323_name_1582706371_314e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F02-26-2020%2Ft_ae2d969d287745a1922d504d42748323_name_1582706371_314e.jpg&h=7d44bfc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14ea317c56b6d7acc334928da9baa8651df40677","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/26/P2020022600477.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F26%2FP2020022600477.htm&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=845327d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/26/P2020022600477.htm</a><br />\n以下是今日（二月二十六日）在立法會會議上蔣麗芸議員的提問和食物及衞生局局長陳肇始教授的書面答覆：<br />\n<br />\n（八）鑑於《職業安全及健康條例》（第&zwj;509章）規定僱主須在合理及切實可行範圍內，確保僱員在工作期間的安全及健康，<span style=\"color: red;\">會否要求僱主在員工工作期間向他們提供足夠的防疫物品</span>（例如口罩及消毒液），若否，原因為何？<br />\n <br />\n（八）根據《職業安全及健康條例》（第509章），僱主須在合理地切實可行範圍內保障其僱員工作時的職業安全及健康（職安健）。因此，每一位僱主均有責任就其僱員的工作進行風險評估，並按風險<span style=\"color: red;\">評估</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />的結果，為其僱員提供所需的裝備以保障他們的職安健。<br />\n </blockquote>"},{"pid":"d990ef974db1cf3b39f1162d4e889b7d05eb0a3d","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaadf0fe086d526ebad5d180bb5d46df0a394061","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb81b9cdcf7aec331e0a1112b3c6cf68e6d8a27","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16139ce1e28157f679b328a05a347dd9902cb2f6","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"各行各業受新冠肺炎影響，打工仔慘被僱主要求放無薪假，甚至減薪。職工盟批評港府提供的援助「到喉唔到肺」，認為政府有責任為失業、開工不足及放無薪假的僱員發放現金津貼，並促請政府將新冠肺炎列為職業病，讓受感染員工可盡快獲得工傷賠償。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31492d04b13f2c264215eefa067a6a34f21597e9","tid":1900391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">勞工處回覆本報查詢，指沒備存僱員被逼放無薪假的統計數字。就被逼扣假無薪的情況，處方鼓勵僱主體恤和諒解僱員的情況，作出彈性處理。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單方面改合約 有權拒絕<br />\n<br />\n就僱主單方面改變上班及支薪安排，職工盟主席吳敏兒提醒，僱員即使面對上司態度強硬，亦毋須懼怕，應跟同事團結及向工會求助，由於未經雙方同意而更改合約屬違法，僱主指定年假清放日期也須十四日前通知僱員，員工有權拒絕及循勞資審裁處控訴，「員工不同意八折支薪會被解僱的這類協議，應視作無效，因這屬不合理解僱；答應跟僱主共渡時艱，也須問清楚減去的薪金日後會否加回來。」<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒直言，目前本港法例對於無薪假未受監管，讓勞資雙方協議引致灰色地帶，長遠須立法作出規管，免卻強弱懸殊，確保無薪假安排不能較原有合約的勞工權益低的情況。"}]}